7f1d4cf22e1d48baebd28725ee099cb878028980af336b6e92d1f580a24a7d11e8b302e2b1f8c14f5b18b1d01313abe43464d8bef631ca18e5b0d613fe0a10a0  fix-ppc64le-isatty.patch"
